ddu_SIS (&506E0)
{f25}Þ{f}	R0 =	Window handle
		R1 =	Icon handle
		R2 =	<Action=>.action>
{f25}Ü{f}	All registers preserved
Not re-entrant.
#line
Set an icon's state
#line
*Basic example*
#fcode;indent 4;wrap off
      SYS "ddu_SIS",Window,Icon,2
#wrap;indent;f
#
#subpage action
ddu_SIS actions
\#	Action
#line
0	make icon shaded
1	make icon normal
2	make icon selected
3	make icon selected and shaded
